ranking_anomalies.name: Electronic musicians
ranking_anomalies.issue: Absurdly high placement of contemporary musicians

assessment.brief_assessment: The list shows strong historical understanding in the top 25, but becomes increasingly erratic and questionable in middle and lower ranks. The bottom 25 is particularly problematic, filled with contemporary musicians with dubious historical significance.
assessment.subjective_impression: This looks like an AI-generated list that starts impressively but gradually descends into randomness and recency bias.
